==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Uppermost
<hw>Up"per*most`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[From
<er>Up</er>, <er>Upper</er>; formed like <ets>aftermost</ets>. Cf.
<er>Upmost</er>.]</ety> <def>Highest in place, position, rank, power, or
the like; upmost; supreme.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Whatever faction happens to be <qex>uppermost</qex>.</q>
<rj><qau>Swift.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Uppertendom</ent>⟦br⟧
